1. Upon launching the application, the user should see a blank background
2. The system shall wait for a touch event to occur to begin activity
3. If a touch event is received, the system shall draw a dot at touch location and begin activity
4. The system shall allow the user to tilt device to control the movement of the dot
5. If the activity has begun, the device shall allow the user to shake the device to reset to background
6. If activity has begun, the system shall prevent dot from reaching bottom edge unless tilt is ~vertical
7. if activity has begun, user places dot in top 20% of screen, system shall display street address in bottom 20% of screen
